---
title: Garlic and Courgette Rigatoni with parsley and creme fraiche
description: A simple and delicious pasta dish, this baked courgette rigatoni features a herby tomato sauce and helpings of melted mozzarella.  If you're a fan of pasta then this is the perfect midweek meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R09_W45_IE_IEXVV17848-3_Main_high-f076d5e9.jpg
